    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi,</p>

<p>The default decorators for ZendX_Jquery form elements are:</p>

<pre><code>        $this-&gt;addDecorator('UiWidgetElement')
             -&gt;addDecorator('Errors')
             -&gt;addDecorator('HtmlTag', array('tag' =&gt; 'dd'))
             -&gt;addDecorator('Label', array('tag' =&gt; 'dt'));
</code></pre>

<p>But should be actually:</p>

<pre><code>        $this-&gt;addDecorator('UiWidgetElement')
             -&gt;addDecorator('Errors')
             -&gt;addDecorator('Description')
             -&gt;addDecorator('HtmlTag', array('tag' =&gt; 'dd'))
             -&gt;addDecorator('Label', array('tag' =&gt; 'dt'));
</code></pre>

<p>So to make the elements defaults compatible with Zend_Form_Element's...</p>

